            <mrow>C \amp = \left\{ {x \in \mathbb{R}\left.  \right|x^2  + 2 = 0} \right\}\!,  \amp   D \amp = \left\{ {x \in \mathbb{R}\left.  \right|x > 0} \right\}\!</mrow>
