      <li>
        <p>
          One of the properties of real numbers is the so-called
          <em>Law of Trichotomy</em>,
            <idx><h>Law of Trichotomy</h></idx>
          which states that if <m>a,
          b \in \R</m>, then exactly one of the following is true:
          <ul>
            <li>
              <p>
                <m>a \lt b</m>;
